.container
  .row
    .col-md-9
      h4.subheader
        | Understanding the city budget by visualizing data, providing a forum for dialogue, and sharing essential information about the budget process.
      div
        img.img-responsive(src='/images/process.png')
        p(align='right')
          small
            | Image:
            a(href='http://www.openspending.org/', target='_blank') OpenSpending
      h2.subheader What we do
      p
        | <strong>Open Budget: Wyoming</strong> promotes a deeper understanding of the city budget, so that citizens, officials, and other stakeholders can engage in more informed dialogue about how the City of Wyoming currently works and how it should in the future.

      h2.subheader How we do it
      ul.disc
      li
        | We work with <strong>community groups</strong> to learn how it would be best shared with the public.
      li
        | We work with the <strong>Wyoming Finance Department</strong> to access budget data and present it in a simple, useful format.
      li
        | We <strong>visualize</strong> Wyoming budget data and share resources for people to create their own visualizations and analyses.
      li
        | We use tools that are <strong>free, open-source, and require minimum technical skill</strong>.
      li
        | We <strong>stimulate dialogue</strong> for Wyoming citizens to discuss the budget.
      p
      | Now that you know our goals,
      a(href='feedback.html')  share your ideas here
      | .
